Please buy a smart watch for me.

I can help with that, but I need a bit more detail to choose the right smartwatch and complete the purchase on your shopping account.

1) Budget range (e.g., $100–$200, up to $500)
2) Phone type and OS:

3) Main priorities (pick a few):  
   - Fitness/health tracking (steps, heart rate, SpO₂, ECG, sleep, stress)  
   - GPS for outdoor runs/rides without phone  
   - Battery life (multi‑day vs fine charging daily)  
   - Smart features (calls, texts, WhatsApp, music, contactless pay)  
   - Style (sporty vs classic, round vs square, metal vs silicone strap)  
4) Any must‑have features:  
   - Waterproof for swimming  
   - Cellular/LTE (use watch without phone nearby)  
   - Specific brand (Apple, Samsung, Garmin, Fitbit, etc.)  
   - Size preference (small wrist / large screen)
5) Shipping constraints:  
   - Country and city  
   - Any preferred marketplace (e.g., Amazon, local store, etc.) if relevant to your account

Once you provide these, I’ll:
- Search for suitable smartwatches
- Add the best option to your cart
- Apply any available discounts
- Complete checkout automatically using your linked payment method.
